WEBVTT

00:00:01.496 --> 00:00:04.391
So you know when
you're doubled over in pain

00:00:04.415 --> 00:00:06.613
and you're wondering, is it your appendix

00:00:06.637 --> 00:00:08.353
or maybe you ate something funny?

00:00:09.472 --> 00:00:13.185
Well, when that happens to me,
I call my friend Sasha --

00:00:13.209 --> 00:00:14.376
Sasha is a doctor --

00:00:14.400 --> 00:00:17.096
and I say, "Should I rush
to the nearest emergency room

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:18.491
in a panic?

00:00:18.515 --> 00:00:21.813
Or am I OK to relax and just wait it out?"

00:00:21.837 --> 00:00:24.900
Yes, I am that annoying friend.

00:00:27.011 --> 00:00:29.416
But in September 2017,

00:00:29.440 --> 00:00:32.726
friends of mine were suddenly calling me